=Description=

"OpenLandLAB is an open source hot spot. 

OLL is a regional experimental space for creatives, social and technologic innovators, artists, 
makers, DIY-activists and„catalysts of the future“ in the Global Village of the open source culture. 
The platform is dual language (german, english) and will be under continous development.

With the next release there will be blogs for discussions."
